The module uses `api_url if api_url is not None else KARAKEEP_API_URL` and `api_key if api_key is not None else KARAKEEP_API_KEY`. When `api_url=None`, it falls back to the module constant which was set at import time. The `api_key=None` falls back to the module constant. So I need to patch the module constants.
